Package com.indus.training.core.impl

package com.indus.training.core.impl
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AgeCalculator
    The AgeCalculator class implements the IAgeCalculator interface to provide the functionality for calculating age based on the provided birth year and current year.
    BMICalculator
    The BMICalculator class implements the IBMICalculator interface to provide the functionality for calculating Body Mass Index (BMI) based on the provided weight and height.
    CelsiusFahrenheitConverter
    The CelsiusFahrenheitConverter class implements the ICelsiusFahrenheitConverter interface to provide functionality for converting temperatures between Celsius and Fahrenheit.
    DistanceConverter
    The DistanceConverter class implements the IDistanceConverter interface to provide functionality for converting distances between kilometers and meters.
    InterestCalculator
    The InterestCalculator class implements the IInterestCalculator interface to provide functionality for calculating simple interest based on the provided principal amount, rate of interest, and time period.
    PercentageCalculator
    The PercentageCalculator class implements the IPercentageCalculator interface to provide functionality for calculating the percentage of a given value.
    PowerOfNumberCalculator
    The PowerOfNumberCalculator class implements the IPowerOfNumberCalculator interface to provide functionality for calculating the power of a number based on the given base and exponent.
